fields.description:
As a user Ill be able to see a splash screen once I open the app:

\-The splash screen will contain a background and an animation.

\-The length of the animation will be determined by Adva.

\-Please make sure that the splash screen contains powered by moveo.

\-At the end of the splash screen, if the user already signed in, he will be transfer to the app main page and if not he will continue to sign in (If the user already signed you need to send a query to the serever to get the app data meanwhile the user is wathcing the splash, Get pateint menus).

fields.description:
As a user which didnt signed up, after the splash screen Ill be transfered to the first sign in page. The page containts:

* Header with the apps logo
* Static welcome title
* Field for entering the users phone number
* Send button

Several comments:

* The send button needs to be disabled and it text needs to be in grey untill the user enters a valid phone number.
* The user will be able to enter only number on the phone number input field
* If the user starts to type a number with the number 972 it will automaticly replaced it to '0'.
* The user will be able to enter only 10 digits number
* If the user entered non valid phone number (with less than 10 digits) when the input field will be unfoucused an error message will appear with the relevant indication.
* after the user type 3 digits a \- will appear after them and the typing will be contiue (if the user delete one of the first three characters it will be deleted too).
* Once the user entres a valid phone number, the send button will be turned to green with a simple chaniging color animation (transitation between two colors).
* Once the user taps on the send button the  text will be replaced with a loader until the callback from the server.

fields.description:
After the user taps on the send button, a query needs to be send to the server. The query will send the  entered phone number and the callback will be:

* Invalid phone number \-stuatus 400, this error should be only on the development period because the client needs to valid the phone number as well
* There is no patient with the entered phone number \-status 400, the app doesnt has a signup flow so if a non registred phone number tries to use the app, he will get an error.
* You will get a phone number immeditly\- status 200 

If you gets an error from the server, you need to stop the loader (revert it into the  text) and show the user the relvent error accroding to the server error.
If you gets 200 from the server you need to transfer the user to the next step.

fields.description:
As a user Ill get a SMS message which contains a validation code and Ill be able to enter it on an input field in order to validate my phone number.

The page contains:

* Header with the apps logo and a back button.
* Static Title in a card
* Input field (with explanation text above it)
* Approve button
* Didnt get an sms button

Several Comments:

* Once the user taps the back button he will be transfered to the first sign in page
* In the input feild the user will be able to enter only numbers and the chars amount will be limited according to the code length (4/6 digits).
* The approve button will be disabled until the user enter a valid validation number.
* The Didnt get sms button will appear only after three seconds.
* Once the user enterd a valid validation number the approve button will be enabled and once the user taps on it, the text will be replaced with a loader.
